  <blockquote>
    <div>
      <strong>⚠️ Slinkity is no longer maintained.</strong> The project owner <a href="https://github.com/bholmesdev">(@bholmesdev)</a> now works on <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> full-time. If you want to build component-driven content sites, give Astro a try! If you're committed to 11ty and want to use client components, consider <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/docs/languages/webc/">11ty's WebC project.</a>
    </div>
  </blockquote>

  <div class="home__heading-link__container">
    <a class="home__heading-link" href="/docs/">Documentation</a>
    <a class="home__heading-link" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/slinkity">npm package</a>
